data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $5000 TOWARDS BUYING YOUR INTEREST RATE DOWN OR TO GO TOWARD OTHER BUYER CLOSING COST!! Don't miss this incentive! Welcome to your 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in McAdory's Letson Farms, offering comfortable living and a vibrant community atmosphere. Inside, spacious living areas and a wonderful kitchen create an inviting environment. The bedrooms are generously sized, and the fenced backyard and screened back patio provide a private outdoor space. Take advantage of neighborhood amenities including a lake, pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, and playground. Experience the perfect balance of cozy living and community convenience in this welcoming neighborhood.
